      "content": "but i've heard that taking them for too long actually causes more harm than good, like it messes with your gut microbiome and drains your immunity. if the infection is visually gone, isn't the extra few days just unnecessary? i'd rather just focus on natural stuff to keep my immune system strong instead of more meds.",
